description:
Morocco is located in the northwest corner of Africa. Thanks to its stunning landscapes, colorful cities, year-round pleasant weather, and unique cuisine, Morocco is a popular travel destination. And although the country is rapidly modernizing, it still retains much of its ancient architecture and even more of its traditional customs. In this video, we’ll highlight 10 amazing places that you should visit in Morocco. 

10. Fez
☑️ Recommended - Guided tour of the old town: https://www.getyourguide.com/fes-l829/fez-medina-4-hour-guided-tour-t75985/?partner_id=57UJ5GF&utm_medium=online_publisher&placement=content-middle&cmp=Fez_video
😴 Recommended - Palais Fes Yahya: https://www.booking.com/hotel/ma/palais-fes-yahya.en.html?aid=7936148&no_rooms=1&group_adults=2
🎥 Fez video: https://youtu.be/aAtHlcWuOhQ

9. Essaouira & the Atlantic Coast
😴 Recommended - Suite Azur Hotel: https://www.booking.com/hotel/ma/suite-azur.en.html?aid=7936148&no_rooms=1&group_adults=2

8. Dades Valley
☑️ Monkey Fingers hike info: https://worldwildhearts.hopp.to/monkey-fingers-hike

7. Chefchaouen
☑️ Recommended - Free walking tour of Chefchaouen: https://worldwildhearts.hopp.to/chefchaouen-walking-tour
🎥 Chefchaouen video: https://youtu.be/yRwftlFoO4Q

6. Marrakech
☑️ Recommended - Free walking tour: https://www.freetour.com/marrakech/exploring-marrakech-old-city-secrets?referralID=ZdvRXrkURXUfA7zT&campaign=Marrakechvideo

🎥 Video Marrakech: https://youtu.be/0NkAE4N8E1A

5. Ouzoud Waterfalls

4. Todra Gorge
☑️ Todra Gorge Hike: https://worldwildhearts.hopp.to/todra-gorge-hike

3. Aït Ben Haddou
